0001.name: Agumon
0001.main_skill: Inflict a small amount of damage to one enemy.
0001.leader_skill: Restores a small portion of your HP.
0001.profile: A cheerful Digimon who uses its hard claws as weapons. Hidden in its small body lies boundless courage, a fearless personality, and an uncharted potential for growth.

0002.name: Gabumon
0002.main_skill: Inflicts a small amount of damage to all enemies.
0002.leader_skill: Small increase in the support power of all allies.
0002.profile: A Digimon that wears Garurumon's fur and is normally very shy. However, wearing the fur inverts its personality and makes it bold. Its weapons are its stiff horn and the sharp claws attached to the fur.

0006.name: Greymon
0006.main_skill: Inflict medium damage to one enemy.
0006.leader_skill: Changes all the brown recovery cards in red dragon cards.
0006.profile: A Digimon with a strong body and a hard, fine horn that boasts high combat power. Its head is covered with a hard shell that increases its defensive ability. It is also skilled at cooperating with its friends in combat.

0007.name: Monochromon
0007.main_skill: Changes all the brown recovery cards in red dragon cards.
0007.leader_skill: Inflict medium damage to one enemy.
0007.profile: A Digimon whose shell and horns are hard as diamond. They say when its horns are completely grown, they will reach half the size of its body. It is an herbivorous and calm Digimon, but when it gets angry it goes on a rampage.

0008.name: Centalmon
0008.main_skill: Changes all the red dragon cards in brown recovery cards.
0008.leader_skill: Inflict medium damage to one enemy.
0008.profile: A Digimon with the upper body of a human and the lower body of an animal. Each part of its body is covered in blue armor. It releases compressed gas through the pipe on its back to help it reach close to the speed of sound.

0009.name: Leomon
0009.main_skill: Inflict medium damage to one enemy.
0009.leader_skill: Medium increase in the attack power of all allies.
0009.profile: A Digimon praised as a noble hero. It is a warrior with a just heart who has defeated many atrocious Digimon. Its rival is Orgemon. On its waist, it carries a magical sword called 'Shishiou-maru'.

0010.name: Garurumon
0010.main_skill: Inflicts medium damage to all enemies.
0010.leader_skill: Adds a small delay to all enemy attacks.
0010.profile: A Digimon covered with fur as hard as mithril. It is feared by other Digimon because it hunts its prey with a carnivore's speed and very precise attacks.

0011.name: Unimon
0011.profile: A synthetic Digimon with a unicorn's horn and a pegasus' wings. Its wings help it fly freely within the network, and its sharp horn helps it fight its enemies. It has a very wild temper.

0016.name: Pandamon
0016.main_skill: Changes all the brown recovery cards in red dragon cards.
0016.profile: A Digimon that looks like a panda but is not very popular because of its bluntness. It pretends to be a maverick, but it secretly yearns to be like the popular Monzaemon. Surprisingly, it is actually very capable.

0017.name: Weregarurumon
0017.main_skill: Inflicts a large amount of damage to all enemies.
0017.leader_skill: Big increase in the attack power of all allies.
0017.profile: A commando-type Digimon that has the leg strength of Garurumon and skilled war tactics. Its jumping abilities are top tier. It has a strong sense of duty and serves its master and partners faithfully.

0018.name: Mammon
0018.main_skill: Only red dragon cards will appear next.
0018.leader_skill: Restores a large portion of your HP.
0018.profile: An ancient Digimon, discovered in the melted ice and snow due to the Digital World warming. On its mask there is a crystal of knowledge which gives it the power of clairvoyance and allows it to see far into the future.

0019.name: Metalgreymon
0019.main_skill: Inflict a large amount of damage to one enemy.
0019.leader_skill: Reduces the damage received by half.
0019.profile: A Digimon with over half of its body mechanized. It is said to have the power of a nuclear warhead. Only a Greymon who has won numerous battles can evolve to this stage.

0020.name: Skullgreymon
0020.main_skill: Inflicts a small amount of damage and restore the same amount of HP.
0020.leader_skill: High decrease in the attack power of all enemies.
0020.profile: A menacing Digimon obsessed with fighting. Thanks to its battle instincts, it continues to fight even though it is nothing but bones. It is feared by other Digimon because it has no intelligence and fights indiscriminately.

0023.name: Saberleomon
0023.main_skill: Inflict most of the damage to one enemy.
0023.leader_skill: Only attack cards will appear next.
0023.profile: An ancient Digimon that is said to be the ancestor of Leomon. It is a huge beast with overwhelmingly destructive claws, strong penetrative tusks, and legs that allow it to run at Mach speed.

0024.name: Baalmon
0024.main_skill: Inflict a large amount of damage to one enemy.
0024.leader_skill: Some purple, brown recovery and wild cards will appear.
0024.profile: An enlightened Digimon called 'The Noble King'. It encompasses all knowledge. The charms attached to its mantle contain the solutions to all possible problems. It serves as general of the Bagra army.

0025.name: Metalgarurumon
0025.main_skill: Inflicts most of the damage to all enemies.
0025.leader_skill: Huge increase in the attack power of red dragon allies.
0025.profile: A Digimon whose whole body is mechanized. It is the final form of Garurumon. It retains Garurumon's speed despite the many heavy firearms attached to its body. It finds its enemies with the laser on the tip of its nose and swiftly shoots them down.

0026.name: Wargreymon
0026.main_skill: Inflict most of the damage to one enemy.
0026.leader_skill: Huge increase in the support power of all allies.
0026.profile: A Digimon equipped with Dramon Killers on both its arms and the Brave Shield on its back. It is a veteran hero wearing armor made of Chrome Digizoid. It has a humanoid shape and is remarkably powerful and fast.

0029.name: Hagurumon
0029.main_skill: Small increase in the defense of all allies.
0029.leader_skill: Inflict a small amount of damage to one enemy.
0029.profile: A mutant Digimon made of a combination of gears. Removing even one gear is enough to make it stop working. It has the deadly skill of manipulating other Digimon, which it uses in mischievous ways.

0030.name: Kokuwamon
0030.main_skill: Inflicts a small amount of damage to all enemies.
0030.profile: A mini insect machine Digimon. It has electricity stored in its body and can use this to even run domestic appliances. In crisis situations, it can release a current of 1 MV to protect its body.

0036.name: Revolmon
0036.main_skill: Changes all the brown recovery cards in blue knight cards.
0036.profile: A Digimon with a strong sense of justice. It belongs to the Virus Busters and deletes evil Digimon. However, since it likes gambling, it pardons evil Digimon who win the Russian roulette.

0037.name: Tankmon
0037.main_skill: Inflict medium damage to one enemy.
0037.leader_skill: Changes all the brown recovery cards in blue knight cards.
0037.profile: A Digimon that enjoys fighting so much its nickname is 'the Mercenary Digimon'. Heavy artillery is installed all throughout its body, which it likes using to shatter its enemies to pieces.

0038.name: Guardromon
0038.main_skill: Medium increase in the defense of all allies.
0038.leader_skill: Slightly reduces the number of turns before a skill is active.
0038.profile: A Digimon with outstanding defense. Originally it was guarding the network with Giromon the net-keeper, but it got infected by a virus and was used by evil Digimon.

0041.name: Knightmon
0041.main_skill: Inflict a large amount of damage to one enemy.
0041.leader_skill: High increase in the defense of all allies.
0041.profile: A loyal Digimon wearing armor made of Chrome Digizoid. It always disregards its own will and obeys the orders of its master. Depending on those orders, it can become either good or evil.

0042.name: Andromon
0042.main_skill: High increase in the defense of all allies.
0042.leader_skill: Increases the value of all cards by 1.
0042.profile: A cyborg Digimon created in an experiment. It has high combat power and strictly follows the orders it receives regardless of their good or evil nature.

0047.name: Mugendramon
0047.main_skill: Inflicts a large amount of damage and restore the same amount of HP.
0047.leader_skill: High increase in the defense of all allies.
0047.profile: A completely metal Digimon that was created by combining the parts of many cyborg Digimon. An evil program is written in its digicore and supplies it with infinite malice.

0054.name: Tentomon
0054.main_skill: Small increase in the attack power of green nature allies.
0054.leader_skill: Small decrease in the attack power of all enemies.
0054.profile: A Digimon with a hard shell but an otherwise very peaceful personality. It is very easygoing and likes smelling the aroma of flowers and taking the occasional nap. It uses its claws deftly and can grab things like a human.

0055.name: Palmon
0055.main_skill: Changes all the brown recovery cards in green nature cards.
0055.leader_skill: Inflicts a small amount of damage and restore the same amount of HP.
0055.profile: A rare type of Digimon that became a plant even though it started evolving like a reptile. A tropical plant blooms on its head and changes scents according to its mood. It buries its feet into the ground in order to absorb nutrients.

0056.name: Gomamon
0056.main_skill: Small decrease in the attack power of all enemies.
0056.leader_skill: Restores a small portion of your HP.
0056.profile: A naughty Digimon that likes pranks. His body is covered with fur so that he can resist to cold temperatures. His claws help him break hard blocks of ice. When he gets angry, the red hair on his head bristles.

0057.name: Piyomon
0057.main_skill: Small decrease in the defense power of all enemies.
0057.leader_skill: Small increase in the defense power of green nature allies.
0057.profile: A Digimon with wings that help it hold things but are unsuitable for flying. It can only fly at the same speed as Patamon. It aspires to someday become Birdramon, who can fly freely in the sky.

0059.name: Kuwagamon
0059.main_skill: Inflicts medium damage to all enemies.
0059.leader_skill: Medium decrease in the defense power of all enemies.
0059.profile: A Digimon of the same maturity as Kabuterimon, its eternal rival. It has well-developed battle instincts. It attacks its prey immediately and grasps it in its scissors.

0060.name: Kabuterimon
0060.main_skill: Medium increase in the attack power of green nature allies.
0060.leader_skill: Medium decrease in the defense power of all enemies.
0060.profile: A powerful insect Digimon with a hard shell. It boasts high defense due to its metallized head. It has no mercy when it attacks its rival Digimon.

0061.name: Birdramon
0061.main_skill: Medium decrease in the defense power of all enemies.
0061.leader_skill: Medium increase in the defense power of green nature allies.
0061.profile: A Digimon dressed in a blazing flame and born of a firewall. It flies freely within the network. Its specialty is air attacks.

0062.name: Togemon
0062.main_skill: Medium increase in the attack power of green nature allies.
0062.leader_skill: Some green nature, brown recovery and wild cards will appear.
0062.profile: A plant Digimon that is easygoing and often absent-minded. However, when somebody upsets it, it angrily brings out its thorn-covered fists.

0066.name: Airdramon
0066.main_skill: Inflict a large amount of damage to one enemy.
0066.leader_skill: Changes all the brown recovery cards in blue knight cards.
0066.profile: An intelligent Digimon that flies freely in the sky. They say that its existence is close to the gods, especially when it calls up storms with its cry. Its fierce personality makes it difficult for ordinary tamers to use.

0068.name: Atlurkabuterimon
0068.main_skill: High increase in the attack power of green nature allies.
0068.leader_skill: High decrease in the defense power of all enemies.
0068.profile: A Digimon discovered in the net area of the tropics. It is an evolved form of Kabuterimon. Its body is about 1.5 times that of Kabuterimon. It's fighting skills have improved thanks to the muscles it developed, but its flying skills dropped.

0070.name: Oukuwamon
0070.main_skill: Inflicts a large amount of damage to all enemies.
0070.leader_skill: High decrease in the defense power of all enemies.
0070.profile: An aggressive Digimon evolved from Kuwagamon. Its scissors have grown even stronger, and its scouting skills have improved due to an enhanced sense of touch. Its defensive abilities, which were not very developed in Kuwagamon, improved as well.

0071.name: Garudamon
0071.main_skill: High decrease in the defense power of all enemies.
0071.leader_skill: Drastically reduces the number of turns before a skill is active.
0071.profile: A Digimon that loves justice and nature. It is the guardian god of earth and wind. Only bird Digimon with high intelligence and fighting ability can evolve into Garudamon. It is a close friend of Leomon, who shares its vision.

0073.name: Megaseadramon
0073.main_skill: Inflicts a small amount of damage and restore the same amount of HP.
0073.leader_skill: Only green nature cards will appear next.
0073.profile: A Digimon with an enlarged head, hard armor, and a blade in the shape of a lightning bolt. It also has a high level of intelligence and a very cautious personality, following its enemies until it brings them down.

0077.name: Heraklekabuterimon
0077.main_skill: Huge increase in the attack power of green nature allies.
0077.leader_skill: Huge decrease in the defense power of all enemies.
0077.profile: An insect Digimon with a shining golden body. It has the features of both Kabuterimon and Kuwagamon. Its weapons are its huge horns and scissors, and it can fly at supersonic speed.

0079.name: Grankuwagamon
0079.main_skill: Inflicts most of the damage to all enemies.
0079.leader_skill: Adds a small delay to all enemy attacks.
0079.profile: A dreadful Digimon called the devil of the deep forest. It is the final form of the Kuwagamon species. It lives in the depths of the forests and is fully nocturnal. Its eternal rival is Heraklekabuterimon.

0080.name: Metalseadramon
0080.main_skill: Huge increase in the defense power of green nature allies.
0080.leader_skill: Some green nature, brown recovery and wild cards will appear.
0080.profile: A Digimon fully covered in Chrome Digizoid alloy. It is the final form of the Seadramon species. It was adapted for use in interception and repels most attacks with its body.

0081.name: Rosemon
0081.main_skill: Inflict most of the damage to one enemy.
0081.leader_skill: Restores a large portion of your HP.
0081.profile: A beautiful female Digimon called the queen of flowers. On its breast it wears a Tiferet, a jewel in which is engraved the symbol of love and beauty. This jewel promises eternal beauty.

0083.name: Impmon
0083.main_skill: Changes all the yellow holy cards in brown recovery cards.
0083.leader_skill: Inflict a small amount of damage to one enemy.
0083.profile: A Digimon that likes pranks and often plays them on electrical products. While it is cruel to its weak opponents, it also stubbornly faces enemies stronger than itself, rather than trying to curry favor with them. Ultimately, this Digimon is quite lonely.

0084.name: Keramon
0084.main_skill: Inflicts a small amount of damage to all enemies.
0084.leader_skill: Small increase in the defense power of purple dark allies.
0084.profile: A child Digimon that thinks destroying data is just a game. It destroys the computers it penetrates, eating away data at a rate of 100MB per second.

0085.name: Candmon
0085.main_skill: Small increase in the attack power of purple dark allies.
0085.leader_skill: Changes all the yellow holy cards in brown recovery cards.
0085.profile: A Digimon with a burning digicore. It cannot survive if its digicore flame dies. For this reason, it is said that its true form is the flame. Although it is a flame-type, it has a calm personality.

0086.name: Picodevimon
0086.main_skill: Inflict a small amount of damage to one enemy.
0086.leader_skill: Increases the value of all cards by 1.
0086.profile: A cunning Digimon that is said to have drawn Devimon to the dark side. It is used by its superiors, Devimon and Vamdemon, and does evil deeds for them.

0087.name: Wizarmon
0087.main_skill: Changes all the brown recovery cards in purple dark cards.
0087.leader_skill: Inflicts a small amount of damage and restore the same amount of HP.
0087.profile: A Digimon that came from Witchelny, a digital world in another dimension, in order to train. It is mastering the magic of earth and fire. It is very shy and doesn't like to show its face.

0088.name: Devimon
0088.main_skill: Inflict medium damage to one enemy.
0088.leader_skill: Changes all the brown recovery cards in purple dark cards.
0088.profile: A fallen angel Digimon. It originally belonged to the angel Digimon but fell to the dark side. It wears the symbol of evil engraved on its chest. It can control other Digimon using its evil intellect and fierce eyes.

0089.name: Bakemon
0089.main_skill: Changes all the brown recovery cards in purple dark cards.
0089.leader_skill: Medium increase in the attack power of purple dark allies.
0089.profile: A ghost Digimon born from the dark area. It is made of a virus program that possesses computers and destroys them. It is said that inside its cloth there is a black hole.

0090.name: Orgemon
0090.main_skill: Increases the value of all cards by 1.
0090.leader_skill: Only attack cards will appear next.
0090.profile: A Digimon hunter with a developed physique and high intelligence. Driven by its rage, it challenges strong Digimon to fight. It is not ashamed of its nickname and holds a bone club as proof that it has defeated Skullgreymon.

0091.name: Meramon
0091.main_skill: Medium increase in the attack power of purple dark allies.
0091.leader_skill: Inflicts a small amount of damage and restore the same amount of HP.
0091.profile: A Digimon whose whole body is shrouded in flames and was born from the firewall that protects the Internet. It has a violent temper, just like the flames that cover its body, and wants to burn everything.

0092.name: Madleomon
0092.main_skill: Only attack cards will appear next.
0092.leader_skill: Inflict a large amount of damage to one enemy.
0092.profile: A frenzy Digimon who lost its own will. It is the result of extensive upgrading in order to obtain power. It relies on its physical strength and poisonous claws as it follows the orders it receives.

0095.name: Bluemeramon
0095.main_skill: High increase in the attack power of purple dark allies.
0095.leader_skill: Inflict a large amount of damage to one enemy.
0095.profile: A flame-type Digimon covered in blue flame. It burns at a higher temperature than Meramon. It has a rough personality and is hard to tame.

0096.name: Deathmeramon
0096.main_skill: High increase in the attack power of purple dark allies.
0096.leader_skill: High increase in the support power of all allies.
0096.profile: A Digimon that overcame water and ice, the weak points of the Meramon species. A blue burning chain winds around its body. Its skilled attacks, defensive abilities, and burning temperature are all enhanced.

0097.name: Fantomon
0097.main_skill: The yellow holy cards will not appear.
0097.leader_skill: Inflicts a large amount of damage to all enemies.
0097.profile: A senior ghost Digimon which has the appearance of the god of death. It searches for its prey using the clairvoyant crystal hanging at its neck. It is said that the interior of the cloth covering its body leads to another dimension.

0098.name: Infermon
0098.main_skill: Inflicts a large amount of damage to all enemies.
0098.leader_skill: High decrease in the defense power of all enemies.
0098.profile: An atrocious Digimon capable of invading any network and destroying its data. Its defense is remarkably improved thanks to the limbs attached to its cocoon body.

0099.name: Ladydevimon
0099.main_skill: Inflict a large amount of damage to one enemy.
0099.leader_skill: Changes all the brown recovery cards in purple dark cards.
0099.profile: A female fallen angel Digimon that holds dark power of incomparable purity. It is impossible to control it using personal computers. Its enemy is Angewomon.

0100.name: Vamdemon
0100.main_skill: Inflict a large amount of damage to one enemy.
0100.leader_skill: High increase in the attack power of purple dark allies.
0100.profile: The king of the Undead Digimon. It was resurrected using dark magic. It is skilled at transforming broken data into evil computer viruses. Its powers are only half as strong during the daytime.

0103.name: Demon
0103.main_skill: Adds a big delay to all enemy attacks.
0103.leader_skill: High increase in the defense of all allies.
0103.profile: One of the Seven Great Demon Lords. It was a high-ranking Angel Digimon, but it was exiled to the darkness after it rebelled against the good world. Now it is planning revenge against the Digital World.

0104.name: Lilithmon
0104.main_skill: Inflict most of the damage to one enemy.
0104.leader_skill: Only purple dark cards will appear next.
0104.profile: A Digimon that was originally a high-ranking Angel Digimon. It fell to the dark side and is now called 'The Goddess of Darkness'. It is one of the Seven Great Demon Lords. Anything touched by the nails of its left hand will corrode.

0107.name: Piemon
0107.main_skill: Only purple dark cards will appear next.
0107.leader_skill: Reduces the damage received from yellow holy enemies.
0107.profile: A Digimon shrouded in mystery. No one knows how or why it was born. It possesses a strong and elusive power, so if you meet it you'll have no choice but to resign yourself to your final moments.

0109.name: Patamon
0109.main_skill: Inflict a small amount of damage to one enemy.
0109.leader_skill: Restores a small portion of your HP.
0109.profile: A Digimon that can fly in the sky due to its big ears. However, its speed is only 1 km/h, so it is faster if it walks. It doesn't wear a Holy Ring, but the genes of ancient Digimon are hidden inside it.

0113.name: Tailmon
0113.leader_skill: Slightly reduces the number of turns before a skill is active.
0113.profile: A Holy Digimon wearing a Holy Ring on its tail. It looks very sweet and innocent, but it has very sharp nails that are copied from Saberleomon's data.

0114.name: Angemon
0114.main_skill: Inflict medium damage to one enemy.
0114.profile: A Digimon whose job is maintaining Good in the Digital World and keeping out Evil. It has six divine wings that are said to bring happiness.

0115.name: Angewomon
0115.main_skill: Restores a large portion of your HP.
0115.leader_skill: High increase in the attack power of yellow holy allies.
0115.profile: A Digimon who has a calm personality but is very strict with twisted and evil individuals. It will punish them until they change. Thanks to its morals and power, it is praised as 'The Goddess' of the Digital World.

0116.name: Holyangemon
0116.main_skill: Inflict a large amount of damage to one enemy.
0116.leader_skill: Restores a large portion of your HP.
0116.profile: A Digimon responsible for surveilling the world as an agent of light. Whenever darkness approaches, it changes to battle mode. It fights the darkness with its sacred sword Excalibur in its right hand and its Beam Shield in its left hand.

0117.name: Goddramon
0117.main_skill: Huge increase in the attack power of yellow holy allies.
0117.leader_skill: Inflict most of the damage to one enemy.
0117.profile: A Holy dragon Digimon with a shining, golden body. It is one of the Four Great Dragons. It is small and wears in its right hand Umon the Blue Thunder, a weapon of regeneration, and in its left hand Amon the Red Flame, a weapon of destruction.

0118.name: Holydramon
0118.leader_skill: Only yellow holy cards will appear next.
0118.profile: A Digimon seated on the highest cliff of the god beast Digimon. It is the master of the skies and has the power to invade anything. It is one of the Four Great Dragons. Legends predict its advent when the evil forces become too strong.

0120.name: Hououmon
0120.main_skill: Huge increase in the defense power of yellow holy allies.
0120.leader_skill: The purple dark cards will not appear.
0120.profile: The head of the bird Digimon. It has four shiny golden wings. It wears two Holy Rings and is said to govern all the Holy Bird Digimon. Its power is immeasurable.
